{"tid":54662,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有250萬可以係世界各地買到什麼樓??","createTime":"2016-12-25T17:27:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-02T10:10:46.000Z","uid":22675,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"568f170f8f4628e1897735486ca4a3fe42d99c49","tid":54662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:27:33.000Z","msg":"芬蘭曼蒂哈爾尤 <br />\n<br />\n帶壁爐的小屋，一個大露臺、兩間臥室、一間浴室、廚房和客廳、桑拿浴室、獨立車庫。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s29.postimg.org/8svh3sppz/8ddc52eb7c567c42030afb044b27dda2_1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs29.postimg.org%2F8svh3sppz%2F8ddc52eb7c567c42030afb044b27dda2_1600max.jpg&h=fbfa7f8c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n多明尼加索蘇<br />\n<br />\n離海岸300米的一間獨棟別墅，3間臥室、3間浴室、一個大廚房/客廳、獨立的更衣室、洗衣房、中央空調系統、游泳池、花園、停車場。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s28.postimg.org/hfobomntp/3a801f7c3f143af7144b936ab086d40b_1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs28.postimg.org%2Fhfobomntp%2F3a801f7c3f143af7144b936ab086d40b_1600max.jpg&h=9001fde8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n義大利萊澤諾 <br />\n<br />\n科莫湖畔一室公寓，湖泊邊景觀房、室內裝飾是天然石材和木材。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/8pnkcp723/6e918c3d28a79ced18a18e093dfd2432_1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2F8pnkcp723%2F6e918c3d28a79ced18a18e093dfd2432_1600max.jpg&h=502a6095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑山 <br />\n<br />\n靠近海邊和市中心的別墅，3層樓、3間臥室、3間浴室、一間廚房和飯廳、一間客廳，一個大露臺、一個花園、一個游泳池。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s29.postimg.org/4aubofg3r/9c10a0abc87073f6d50a7d1e5b4122ca_1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs29.postimg.org%2F4aubofg3r%2F9c10a0abc87073f6d50a7d1e5b4122ca_1600max.jpg&h=ebbb1e62&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n西班牙奧利瓦 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3間臥室、2間浴室、廚房、一間客廳、一個室內停車庫、4個車位。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s30.postimg.org/nve1ml8z5/52dfc952e0739ae81f3b2eb8b2e0a7d3_1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs30.postimg.org%2Fnve1ml8z5%2F52dfc952e0739ae81f3b2eb8b2e0a7d3_1600max.jpg&h=bfb6624b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國洛杉磯 <br />\n<br />\n薩莫拉大道小別墅，3間臥室、1個浴室、1個客廳。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s30.postimg.org/48xbh3ua9/cab113ef643ae3c7f9900bce7801cbc8_1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs30.postimg.org%2F48xbh3ua9%2Fcab113ef643ae3c7f9900bce7801cbc8_1600max.jpg&h=146b99c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n土耳其安塔利亞 <br />\n<br />\n凱梅爾獨棟別墅，3間臥室、3間浴室、一個美國式廚房、一間桑拿浴室和一個露臺。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s28.postimg.org/iidfp5c31/30f38f862708bdd25923f8f79efa24ba_1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs28.postimg.org%2Fiidfp5c31%2F30f38f862708bdd25923f8f79efa24ba_1600max.jpg&h=2247843d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法國布列塔尼 <br />\n<br />\n朗代比阿老式別墅，一個廚房和飯廳、客廳、7間臥室、4間浴室、暖氣系統。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s29.postimg.org/r2e3milrb/5766e1e50ae6d606c7eabd7e7d3e0b1f_1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs29.postimg.org%2Fr2e3milrb%2F5766e1e50ae6d606c7eabd7e7d3e0b1f_1600max.jpg&h=e503460c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n克羅埃西亞波雷奇 <br />\n<br />\n在度假區一個安靜的別墅，一個廚房和客廳、3間臥室、2間浴室、一個帶壁爐屋頂的露臺、中央空調、中央供暖系統。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s27.postimg.org/6m1h2tc83/d42b4c0d097d62f5cded47f461fd2e5c_1600max.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs27.postimg.org%2F6m1h2tc83%2Fd42b4c0d097d62f5cded47f461fd2e5c_1600max.jpg&h=7e2d869b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ab30956c6c5eb129f2f46b8ca066aee675de27b","tid":54662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:28:29.000Z","msg":"臺北 <br />\n<br />\n只能買到文山區的30年老屋，坪數有27.95坪。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s28.postimg.org/s2hzvjhnx/71059b03e8a6fbce5b0eaf233441987b_1600max.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs28.postimg.org%2Fs2hzvjhnx%2F71059b03e8a6fbce5b0eaf233441987b_1600max.png&h=2b529f6d&s={SIZE}\" />[/url] <br />\n<br />\n香港 <br />\n<br />\n香港的房價真的不是一般的高！1000萬新臺幣只能買到下面的房子。 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s24.postimg.org/rsne2k911/590408383df13f7ba7a9ef2c2d314f15_1600max.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs24.postimg.org%2Frsne2k911%2F590408383df13f7ba7a9ef2c2d314f15_1600max.png&h=5a236741&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"38ed5bb83decdd4d032a01837fa8961c4a264fda","tid":54662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T17:30:00.000Z","msg":"得罪講句 <br />\n香港樓貴係因為轉手快容易令資產增值 <br />\n有2球半就算買到世外桃源都係退休先享用 <br />\n這就是港奴式香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40b0fe21f95023d6a3ad547319ce188e3469bdc5","tid":54662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81cb393f3d88bcc56033d52a75363dde57ce9511","tid":54662,"uid":39207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-25T18:38:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6146b881183e6258d38804ce10cda13d7d504a6f","tid":54662,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:08:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b79f1f46eaa32b340249d0fd5b2e0b74f1d240c","tid":54662,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T01:15:27.000Z","msg":"兩舊半劏房都買唔到"},{"pid":"f7f1bbfa3e6ca9f6dc25096b3760a5f1ce8f2b1f","tid":54662,"uid":34773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:11:35.000Z","msg":"香港只買到車房"},{"pid":"0e0e0912f63c382c07a16029b83ac2ee1ed3267e","tid":54662,"uid":21122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:14:08.000Z","msg":"車位都60-100萬啦<br />\n250萬想買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6660da73f9257e1d09449acc0473c2e073cdda6","tid":54662,"uid":342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-26T02:16:52.000Z","m